OL,6,FGlenrothes in Scotland has been
OL,7,Fidentified by a property website as
OL,8,FBritain's most popular affordable town
OL,9,Ffor families.
OL,11,FSituated in the heart of Fife, and
OL,12,Fwithin commuting distance to
OL,13,FEdinburgh, Glenrothes is nestled among
OL,14,Fbeautiful landscapes.
OL,16,FZoopla measured affordability by
OL,17,Flooking at the ratio of average three-
OL,18,Fbed house prices in locations,
OL,19,Fcompared with average earnings in the
OL,20,Flocal authority area.
