OL,6,FIts popularity ranking was based on
OL,7,Fthe average number of Zoopla listing
OL,8,Fviews for a typical three-bed home in
OL,9,Feach area, with the research based on
OL,10,Fthe first quarter of 2025.
OL,12,FThe website also commissioned a survey
OL,13,Fof 2,000 people across the UK by
OL,14,FOpinium in April, which found around a
OL,15,Fthird (34%) of people fear being
OL,16,Fpriced out of their ideal family home
OL,17,Flocation.
OL,19,FScotland and Wales dominated the list
OL,20,Fof the most popular towns in Zoopla's
OL,21,Ftop 10.
